text: Hello, have you ever made a charitable donation?
Yes I have
Which charity have you donated to?
Save the children
That is such a great organization isn't it? I love donating to their worthy cause, don't you?
Yes. Save the children is a very nice organization
What is the most that you have donated to them?
I donated 1000 dollars to them.
WOW! That's great! Was it a one time donation or continuous?
I do it once a year
Great! So, what if i told you that you that i could help you donate an even smaller amount to Save the Children right now. Would you do it?
Sure I would
That's great! The great part is that it can be any amount that you would like to donate. Sound fair?
Yes. I would like to make a donation
That's great! How much would you like to donate today?
I would like to donate 5 dollars.
That's a perfect amount!
Do you have the link to the site
I sure do as a matter of fact it's  URL On behalf of Save the children i would like to say thank you for your donation and have a great day!
Thank you. You too
